## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not reflect the most current developments in China's digital economy. Additionally, the sources used may have inherent biases, particularly those from state-affiliated media. The analysis is limited to the information accessible through the selected search strategy and may not encompass all aspects of China's digital economy advancements.